{"tid":2415661,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"堅尼地城 高先電影院(Golden Scene) 位置","createTime":"2021-02-20T12:07:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T04:15:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dea0b8ce63e048089db280409741e9d710996bf7","tid":2415661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:07:41.000Z","msg":"堅尼地城 高先電影院(Golden Scene) 位置<br />\n<br />\nA 283-seat independent cinema in Kennedy Town<br />\n<br />\nThe Western district welcomes a new independent cinema in Kennedy Town just in time as entertainment venues reopen in the city. Located at Catchick Street and North Street's intersection, the four-house cinema Golden Scene officially opens its doors on February 18. The local film distributor will be showcasing art films, Hong Kong-made films, and international blockbusters.<br />\n<br />\nsource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timeout.com/hong-kong/art/golden-scene-cinema\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeout.com%2Fhong-kong%2Fart%2Fgolden-scene-cinema&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=7d3fc43b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.timeout.com/hong-kong/art/golden-scene-cinema</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMs0nWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMs0nWc.png&h=43f6a1ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n嗰度有條好靚既海濱長廊一直可以行到去上環信德中心, 睇完戲記得行吓,<br />\n簡直嘆為觀止, 身心舒暢.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BwV5y5k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBwV5y5k.png&h=26737ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4V9aKZW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4V9aKZW.png&h=f52917c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n======================<br />\n<br />\n眾聞<br />\n曾發行《十年》投資小眾題材 高先電影院西環落成 曾麗芬盼觀眾有選擇<br />\n<br />\n撰文: 記者張凱傑 | 發佈日期: 18.02.21<br />\n<br />\n「我想做社區戲院，而不是大型院線，我們很久沒有在街上看見戲院，而不是在商場內。」高先電影的靈魂人物曾麗芬，夢想開設社區戲院數十載，今天香港空間受壓、疫情未明的環境下，在堅尼地城吉席街圓夢，落成首間自家戲院，破釜沉舟。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人稱Winnie的高先電影董事總經理曾麗芬，多年來發行和投資題材偏門及關注小眾議題的本土電影。張凱傑攝<br />\n<br />\n做過買片、賣片、。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由於原址不是電影院，沒有走火通道、消防系統，也要增設電梯、樓梯、水缸。由2019年10月簽約，一共改了四次圖則，方通過消防條例，一年多後才落成。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。，「個個都推你，這個時勢很艱難，又或者他們不看好這個地區。」<br />\n<br />\n堅持下去，是因為「我想挑戰自己，我會做得好好，好的電影應該要有好的戲院做，得到較長的放映期。」<br />\n<br />\n「我想香港、九龍、新界，各有一間戲院，是社區戲院，而不是大型院線，我們很久沒有在街上看見戲院而不是在商場內，我們想在街上看見很大的招牌，有少許懷舊的味道，但入面又很新。」<br />\n<br />\n跟其他院線不同，她希望觀眾「入到來有好多選擇，不止我喜歡的藝術片，也有好的商業片，老少咸宜，一定找到自己喜歡的電影。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/news_新聞/hk-discuss/2021/02/曾麗芬-高先電影-20210218212117_24b1_small.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Fnews_%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%2Fhk-discuss%2F2021%2F02%2F%E6%9B%BE%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%AC-%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-20210218212117_24b1_small.jpg&h=eb45b62c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高先電影院坐落堅尼地城吉席街。<br />\n<br />\n高先電影院的股東（左起）：曾憲玟、王利民、曾麗芬、郭秉鑫、梁邵斌<br />\n<br />\n高先電影有限公司（Golden Scene）曾發行政治題材電影《十年》、投資《幻愛》、《淪落人》、《叔叔》、《那夜凌晨，我坐上了旺角開往大埔的紅VAN》等多套香港本土電影，部分關注小眾題材，在堅尼地城吉席街落成自家戲院後，發行和放映電影上將不再受其他院線限制。<br />\n<br />\n高先電影院樓高兩層，設有四個放映院，合共280個觀眾席，首部上映的電影《狂舞派3》，在去年台灣金馬獎上，唱作人用廣東話夾雜英文唱出這首電影主題曲，當中包括以下幾句：<br />\n<br />\nEveryone hears the voice （每個人都聽到訴求）<br />\nEveryone makes the choice （每個人都作出選擇）<br />\nTo bring the glory to us all （願榮耀歸於我們）<br />\n<br />\n其中一位投資者說道：「香港電影我們自己上映。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n了解「讚賞公民計劃」<br />\n<br />\n請加入成為眾新聞的月費訂戶，長期支持我們的工作。所有訂戶都可以收到我們的「每周時事」通訊 。<br />\n<br />\n月費訂戶網址：<a href=\"http://hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkcnews.com%2Faboutus%2F%23subscribe&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=97a0a7bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hkcnews.com/aboutus/#subscribe</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38311/高先電影-golden_scene-曾麗芬-38311/曾發行《十年》投資小眾題材-高先電影院西環落成-曾麗芬盼觀眾有選擇\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F38311%2F%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1-golden_scene-%E6%9B%BE%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%AC-38311%2F%E6%9B%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A1%8C%E3%80%8A%E5%8D%81%E5%B9%B4%E3%80%8B%E6%8A%95%E8%B3%87%E5%B0%8F%E7%9C%BE%E9%A1%8C%E6%9D%90-%E9%AB%98%E5%85%88%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E9%99%A2%E8%A5%BF%E7%92%B0%E8%90%BD%E6%88%90-%E6%9B%BE%E9%BA%97%E8%8A%AC%E7%9B%BC%E8%A7%80%E7%9C%BE%E6%9C%89%E9%81%B8%E6%93%87&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=da14b087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/38311/高先電影-golden_scene-曾麗芬-38311/曾發行《十年》投資小眾題材-高先電影院西環落成-曾麗芬盼觀眾有選擇</a>"},{"pid":"3536332848edb80de56442e5aec819335e986290","tid":2415661,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9808b04f2d477908346694af4a503d4f7f9dab3","tid":2415661,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"白痴問題, 係咪細院?"},{"pid":"8e2b027df47cf43bdbdd40b335640d4f3ca0feb4","tid":2415661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"b9808b04f2d477908346694af4a503d4f7f9dab3","tid":2415661,"uid":156913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:16:14.000Z","msg":"白痴問題, 係咪細院?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"#1<br />\n<br />\nA <span class=\"orange\">283-seat</span> independent cinema in Kennedy Town<br />\n<br />\nThe Western district welcomes a new independent cinema in Kennedy Town just in time as entertainment venues reopen in the city. Located at Catchick Street and North Street's intersection, <span class=\"orange\">the four-house cinema</span> Golden Scene officially opens its doors on February 18. The local film distributor will be showcasing art films, Hong Kong-made films, and international blockbusters.<br />\n<br />\nsource :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.timeout.com/hong-kong/art/golden-scene-cinema\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeout.com%2Fhong-kong%2Fart%2Fgolden-scene-cinema&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkrM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=7d3fc43b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.timeout.com/hong-kong/art/golden-scene-cinema</a>"},{"pid":"50e865bbb21b7f7a4d54eac12ce62c8c56083b3c","tid":2415661,"uid":9,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"屌你,住西環想睇戲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁樣call馬 點有位呀"},{"pid":"477763042bb2e53a46aba123695fdba8572a481c","tid":2415661,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:12:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14ef965184d932e9471a10d725de0f9454983cc9","tid":2415661,"uid":40979,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:14:12.000Z","msg":"依間真係黃色戲院<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6886277c4abf776a55cd155d3742f4d67cbdf8b1","tid":2415661,"uid":60924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"50e865bbb21b7f7a4d54eac12ce62c8c56083b3c","tid":2415661,"uid":9,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"屌你,住西環想睇戲呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咁樣call馬 點有位呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-21T05:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />call  唔call都冇位"},{"pid":